<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","className":"margin-top-half"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center margin-top-half">Our Organic Farm's History</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:separator {"opacity":"css"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-css-opacity"/>
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center has-background-color has-text-color"><em>Ten years ago we transplanted our first Onugbu plant in the rich soil of our farm house located in Gauteng, South Africa. Ever since then our crops have thrived and multiplied without the use of harmful pesticides, synthetic fertilizes and genetic engineering. Our responsibility as your bitter leaf supplier is to deliver our greens on time in excellent condition.&nbsp;</em></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

